me.eddie.inventoryguiapi.gui.contents

Class GUIPopulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.eddie.inventoryguiapi.gui.contents.GUIPopulator

  • public class GUIPopulator
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for Calculating the positions that GUIElements need to go into in the displayed inventory, adding page changing buttons if necessary and then updating the current inventory state. To customize an inventory layout beyond what this is capable of, simply extend this class and make your GUI use your extended version of GUIPopulator.
